export const PorcoRossoComendoSVG = () => {
  return (
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="1000" height="600"
    viewBox="0 0 5 5">
  <rect id="black"
       fill="#000"
       width="5"
       height="3"/>
  <rect id="gray_i"
       fill="#444"
       width="5"
       height="2" y="1"/>
  <rect id="gray_ii"
       fill="#888"
       width="5"
       height="1" y="2"/>
  <rect id="gray_iii"
       fill="#ccc"
       width="5"
       height="1" y="3"/>
  <rect id="white"
       fill="#fff"
       width="15"
       height="1" y="4"/>
</svg>
  );
};
